<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Nih Cok!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #3e2723; /* Coklat tua */
      color: #f5f5dc; /* Warna krem */
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #ffcc80; /* Coklat terang */
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #ffe0b2;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .buttons a {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #6d4c41;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .buttons a:hover {
      background-color: #8d6e63;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Nih Cok!</h1>
  <p>Cokelat premium, manisnya bikin jatuh cinta. Temukan rasa terbaik di setiap gigitan.</p>
  <div class="buttons">
    <a href="/login">Sign In</a>
    <a href="/register">Sign Up</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
